b)).125,126 In fact, the particle focusing effect of viscoelastic fluids in microchannels involves many factors, such as channel shape, Wi, Re, El, particle diameter or even the external fields (magnetic, acoustic, electric fields, etc.), the details of which are not in the scope of this paper.
